(626, 107, '_form', 'Symposium Travel Grant Application (select all that apply; mileage limit applies only to Travel Assistance Grant*) *<br/>\n[checkbox checkbox-193 \"Symposium Grant I: Travel Assistance Grant (must be more than 75 miles distant from Oxford, MS)\" \"Symposium Grant II: Registration Grant ($30.00)\" \"Symposium Grant III: Supplementary Substitute Grant (must provide a receipt or official record of substitute pay)\" \"Symposium Grant IV: CEU Registration Grant Assistance ($20.00)\"]\n\n<em>*Maximum Travel Award: $100.00</em>\n\nUse the space below to tell us how the travel grant will benefit you.<br/>\n[textarea textarea-174]\n\nPlease provide your arrival and departure dates (mm/dd/yy)<br/>\nArrival: [text text-701]\nDeparture: [text text-953]\n\nTo apply for one of the above grant opportunities, complete the appropriate fields below, especially any required, and submit by using the SEND button below. You will receive an email confirmation from us; award announcements will be made at the Friday breakfast on Friday October 2, 2015.<br/>\n\nName (required)<br />\n  [text text-39] \n\nEmail (required)<br />\n [text text-114] \n\nAddress (required)<br />\n[textarea textarea-883]\n\nInstitution (required)<br />\n  [text text-209] \n\n<p>[submit \"Send\"]</p>'),
