(400, 9, '2012-09-13 19:18:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'For most of the day on Friday, we will be meeting in the Student Union. The closest visitor parking (shown in pink) to this location is found on the circle. We will have someone in a Transitioning t-shirt positioned <strong>near the entrance to the circle with parking passes on Friday</strong>. You can pick up your pass,park in the visitor parking, and then walk to the Student Union.\n\nOn Saturday, we will be in the Butler Auditorium, which is part of the Inn at Ole Miss. It is the large unlabeled set of buildings behind the Alumni Center on the map. If you are staying at the Inn, you will be able to walk through the hotel to the auditorium. Those of you who will be driving in, we will have <strong>parking passes available at the Inn at Ole Miss front desk on Saturday morning</strong>.\n\n<a href=\"http://130.74.44.156/transitioning/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/Union12.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-501\" src=\"http://130.74.44.156/transitioning/wp-content/uploads/2012/09/Union12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"600\" /></a>', 'Parking', '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '2012-09-13 19:18:19', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 16, 'http://transitioning.olemiss.edu/?page_id=400', 1, 'page', '', 0),
