(21, 8, '2012-05-08 18:25:50', '2012-05-08 18:25:50', 'The Transitioning symposium will be held on Friday, October 10 and Saturday, October 11, 2014 (there is no home Ole Miss football game scheduled this weekend). The symposium will begin Friday morning and end with a working luncheon on Saturday. Our program has been developed by a committee of teachers of writing from area high schools, community colleges, and the University of Mississippi.\r\n\r\nA copy of the Symposium schedule will be available soon.', 'Events', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'events', '', '', '2014-08-01 21:46:28', '2014-08-01 21:46:28', '', 0, 'http://transitioning.olemiss.edu/?page_id=21', 0, 'page', '', 0),
