(1026, 1, '2014-08-01 13:39:29', '2014-08-01 13:39:29', 'Please complete the form below to register for the Transitioning to College Writing Symposium. When you have submitted your registration information, you will receive a confirmation email. Please print this email for your records.\r\n\r\n<strong>Registration Fee: </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Friday Only - $30</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Saturday Only - $30</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Friday and Saturday - $50</strong>\r\n\r\nPlease send your payment by check to:\r\n\r\nDept. of Writing and Rhetoric\r\nAttn: Joanne Mitchell\r\nP.O. Box 1848\r\nLamar Hall, 3rd Floor, Suite B\r\nUniversity, MS 38655\r\n\r\nAfter registering, you will be added to the Transitioning listserv so that we can send you alerts and announcements via email. If you do not want to be added to the listserv, send an email to <a href=\"mailto:cwr@olemiss.edu\">cwr@olemiss.edu.</a>\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions about this form, please contact us at <a href=\"mailto:cwr@olemiss.edu\">cwr@olemiss.edu</a> or (662) 915-2121.\r\n\r\n[contact-form-7 id=\"80\" title=\"Registration Form\"]', 'Registration', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '77-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-08-01 13:39:29', '2014-08-01 13:39:29', '', 77, 'http://130.74.44.156/transitioning/?p=1026', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(80, 1, '2012-05-15 18:30:20', '2012-05-15 18:30:20', '<label for=\"firstname\">First Name\r\n[text* text-55 id:firstname class:firstname]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"lastname\">Last Name\r\n[text* text-909 id:lastname class:lastname]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"youremail\">Your Email\r\n    [email* your-email id:youremail]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"institution\">Institution/Organization\r\n[text text-345 id:institution]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"position\"> Title/Position\r\n[text text-289 id:position]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"phone\">Phone\r\n[text text-348 id:phone]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"address1\">Mailing Address\r\n[text text-504 id:address1]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"address2\">Mailing Address 2\r\n[text text-655 id:address2]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"city\">City\r\n[text text-324 id:city]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"zip\">Zip Code\r\n[text text-36 id:zip]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"state\">State\r\n[select menu-893 id:state \"Mississippi\" \"Tennessee \" \"Louisiana \" \"Alabama\" \"Georgia \" \"Other\"]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"whoareyou\">Who are you?\r\n[select* menu-619 id:whoareyou \"Program Planner/Participant\" \"High School English or Language Arts Teacher\" \"English or Writing Instructor\" \"English or Writing Professor\" \"Educator (includes administrators)\" \"Writing Center Administrator\" \"Writing Tutor/Consultant\" \"Student\" \"Graduate Student\" \"Vendor\" \"Other\"]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"other\">If other, please describe: \r\n[text text-644 id:other]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"wctutors\">If you are a writing teacher or writing center director bringing students with you, please list their names in order for us to have name badges ready when you arrive.\r\n[textarea textarea-574 id:wctutors]\r\n<em>Students may attend all sessions for free, but please add $10 for each student to your registration payment if students will be eating conference meals.</em> \r\n\r\n<label for=\"diet\">Please list any food allergies, special diets, or other dining considerations you would like to request.\r\n[text text-4 id:diet]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"meals\">Will you attend the Thursday night reception?\r\n[radio radio-399 id:meals class:meals \"Yes\" \"No\"]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"parking\">Will you be bringing a car to campus for the symposium? (If you register after September 28, you may pick up your parking pass when you arrive at the symposium. Parking for both days is included in the cost of registration.)\r\n[radio radio-145 id:parking class:parking use_label_element \"Yes\" \"No\"]\r\n\r\n<label for=\"ceucredits\">Will you apply for CEU credit based on your symposium attendance?\r\n[radio radio-750 id:ceucredits class:ceucredits use_label_element \"Yes\" \"No\"]\r\n<em>If you will be applying for CEU credit, there will be a $20 fee for processing the credit. You will be given the form and directions when you pick up your welcome bag and name badge at the registration desk. </em>\r\n<br/>\r\n<label for=\"payment\">How will you be paying for registration?\r\n[select* menu-567 id:payment class:payment \"PayPal (below)\" \"Mailed Check\" \"Purchase Order\" \"In-Person\"]\r\n<br/>\r\n[submit \"Send\"]\r\nAfter Registration, you will receive a confirmation email with further instructions.\nRegistration for Transitioning to College Writing\n[your-name] <[your-email]>\nDear [text-55] [text-909]:\r\n\r\nWe have received your registration for the 2015 Transitioning to College Writing Symposium. \r\n\r\nWe recommend you to bring a copy of your completed registration form with you to the conference. \r\n\r\n\r\nRegistration Information: \r\n\r\nFirst Name: [text-55]\r\n\r\nLast Name: [text-909]\r\n\r\nEmail: [your-email]\r\n\r\nInstitution: [text-345]\r\n\r\nTitle: [text-289]\r\n\r\nPhone: [text-348]\r\n\r\nAddress: [text-504]\r\n\r\nAddress 2: [text-655]\r\n\r\nCity: [text-324]\r\n\r\nZip: [text-36]\r\n\r\nState: [menu-893]\r\n\r\nAttendee Type: [menu-619]\r\n\r\nOther Attendee Type: [text-644]\r\n\r\nAccompanying Students: [textarea-574]\r\n\r\nThursday Reception?: [radio-399]\r\n\r\nDiet Preferences: [text-4]\r\n\r\nAre you driving to campus? [radio-145]\r\n\r\nAre you applying for CEU credits? [radio-750]\r\n\r\nHow will you pay for registration?\r\n[menu-567]\r\n\r\nPlease contact the Department of Writing and Rhetoric at rhetoric@olemiss.edu or call 662-915-2121 if you have any questions. \r\n--\r\nThis mail is sent from Transitioning to College Writing http://transitioning.olemiss.edu\n<transitioning@olemiss.edu>, <joanne4d@gmail.com>, [your-email]\n\n\n1\n\n\n[your-subject]\n[your-name] <[your-email]>\nMessage body:\r\n[your-message]\r\n\r\n--\r\nThis mail is sent via contact form on Transitioning to College Writing http://transitioning.olemiss.edu\n[your-email]\n\n\n\n\nYour message was sent successfully. Thanks.\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact the administrator by another method.\nValidation errors occurred. Please confirm the fields and submit it again.\nPlease accept the terms to proceed.\nEmail address seems invalid.\nPlease fill the required field.\nFailed to upload file.\nThis file type is not allowed.\nThis file is too large.\nFailed to upload file. Error occurred.\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact the administrator by another method.\nYour entered code is incorrect.\nYour answer is not correct.\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact the administrator by another method.\nURL seems invalid.\nTelephone number seems invalid.\nDate format seems invalid.\nThis date is too early.\nThis date is too late.\nNumber format seems invalid.\nThis number is too small.\nThis number is too large.\nThis input is too long.\nThis input is too short.', 'Registration Form', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'contact-form-1-2', '', '', '2015-09-01 15:57:17', '2015-09-01 15:57:17', '', 0, 'http://transitioning.olemiss.edu/wpcf7_contact_form/contact-form-1/', 0, 'wpcf7_contact_form', '', 0),
