(624, 1, '2013-01-25 15:49:26', '2013-01-25 15:49:26', '<h4>Your Name\n\n    [text* your-name] </h4>\n\n\n<h4>Your Email\n\n    [email* your-email] </h4>\n\n\n<h4>Select Registration\n\n[select menu-699 \"Friday and Saturday Registration (1.25 CEU Credits) --  $50.00\" \"Friday Only Registration (0.75 CEU Credits) -- $30.00\" \"Saturday Only Registration -- $25.00\"]</h4>\n\n<h4>Are you a vendor?\n\n[radio radio-215 \"Yes\" \"No\"]</h4>\n\n\n<h4>Will you be attending Friday\'s breakfast (7:30am - 8:30am)?\n\n[radio radio-929 \"Yes\" \"No\"]</h4>\n\n\n<h4>Will you be attending Saturday\'s breakfast (7:30am - 8:30am)?\n\n[radio radio-661 \"Yes\" \"No\"]</h4>\n\n\n<h4>Friday Tour Preference\n\n[select menu-579 \"Double Decker Bus Tour\" \"Writing Center Tour\"\"Library Archives Tour\" \"No Tour\"]</h4>\n\n\n<h4>Will you be attending the Friday night video presentation and discussion (5:15pm - 6:30pm)?\n\n[radio radio-456 \"Yes\" \"No\"]</h4>\n\n\n<h4>Do you have any dietary restrictions or special dining preferences? </h4>\n\n[text text-4]</h4>\n<em>Please list any food allergies, special diets, or other dining considerations you would like to request. </em>\n\n<h4>T-Shirt Size\n\n[select menu-320 \"Small\" \"Medium\" \"Large\" \"Extra-Large\" \"XX-Large\"]</h4>\n\n\n<h4>Institution/Organization\n\n[text text-345]</h4>\n\n\n<h4>Title/Position\n\n[text text-289]</h4>\n\n\n<h4>Phone\n\n[text text-348]</h4>\n\n\n<h4>Address\n\n[text text-504]</h4>\n\n\n<h4>Address 2\n\n[text text-655]</h4>\n\n\n<h4>City\n\n[text text-324]</h4>\n\n\n<h4>Zip Code\n\n[text text-36]</h4>\n\n\n<h4>State\n\n[select menu-893 \"Mississippi\" \"Tennessee \" \"Louisiana \" \"Alabama\" \"Georgia \" \"Other\"]</h4>\n\n\n<p>After Registration, you will receive a confirmation email with further instructions. \n\n<strong>Print your confirmation email and send with your check to:</strong>\nJoanne Mitchell \nCenter for Writing and Rhetoric\nUniversity of Mississippi\nPO Box 1848\n100 Somerville Hall\nUniversity, MS 38677\n</p>\n<p>Please make check or money order payable to: \n<strong>UNIVERSITY OF MISSISSIPPI</strong>\n</p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Enter the security code then submit your selection\n   [captchac captcha-27]<br />\n[captchar captcha-27]</p>\n\n<p>[submit \"Send\"]</p>\nRegistration for Transitioning to College Writing\n[your-name] \nDear [your-name]:\n\nWe have received your registration for the 2012 Transitioning to College Writing Symposium. Please print this email and mail it with a check for the correct registration amount to:\n\nJoanne Mitchell \nCenter for Writing and Rhetoric\nUniversity of Mississippi\nPO Box 1848\n100 Somerville Hall\nUniversity, MS 38677\n\n\nCheck Number: ___________\n\nNote: \n1. Please make check (drawn on a US bank) or money order payable to: UNIVERSITY OF MISSISSIPPI\n2. We recommend you to bring a copy of your completed registration form with you to the conference. \n\n\nRegistration Information: \n\nName:[your-name]\n\nEmail: [your-email]\n\nRegistration: [menu-699]\n\nVendor? [radio-215]\n\nFriday Breakfast: [radio-929]\n\nSaturday Breakfast: [radio-661]\n\nTour Preference: [menu-579]\n\nVideo Presentation: [radio-456]\n\nDining Preferences: [text-4]\n\nT-Shirt Size: [menu-320]\n\nInstitution: [text-345]\n\nTitle: [text-289]\n\nPhone: [text-348]\n\nAddress: [text-504]\n\nAddress 2: [text-655]\n\nCity: [text-36]\n\nState: [menu-893]\n\nPlease contact the Center for Writing and Rhetoric at cwr@olemiss.edu or call 662-915-2121 if you have any questions. \n--\nThis mail is sent from Transitioning to College Writing http://transitioning.olemiss.edu\n, [your-email]\n\n\n1\n\n[your-subject]\n[your-name] \nMessage body:\n[your-message]\n\n--\nThis mail is sent via contact form on Transitioning to College Writing http://transitioning.olemiss.edu\n[your-email]\n\n\n\nYour message was sent successfully. Thanks.\nFailed to send your message. Please try later or contact the administrator by another method.\nValidation errors occurred.