llstablesbedandbreakfast.com/\">Oak Hill Stables</a></strong>\r\n(662) 801-2084 • 670 County Road 101 (off Old Hwy.7)\r\n\r\n<strong><a href=\"http://www.oxfordravine.com/\">Ravine</a></strong>\r\n(662) 234-4555 • 53 CR 321\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://thez-oxford.com/page8.php\"><strong>The Z Bed and Breakfast</strong></a>\r\n(713)927-1295 • 1405 Pierce Ave\r\n\r\n[/expand]\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>Parking</h2>\r\nIf you indicate on the registration page that you will be bringing a car, a parking pass will be mailed to you before the conference. The closest visitor parking to our events will be on the Circle by the Grove. Click the map below to view all the visitor parking areas.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://transitioning.olemiss.edu/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Visitor-Parking-Map.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-1066 size-medium\" src=\"http://transitioning.olemiss.edu/wp-content/uploads/2012/05/Visitor-Parking-Map-300x194.jpg\" alt=\"Visitor Parking Areas\" width=\"300\" height=\"194\" /></a>', 'Lodging and Travel', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '16-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-11-20 20:11:06', '2014-11-20 20:11:06', '', 16, 'http://transitioning.olemiss.edu/16-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
