"text-align: center;\"><strong>Lunch and Closing Session\r\nViewing of selected <em>Take 20</em> clips\r\nPlanning for 2013 - </strong>announcements and dates to save</p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Program', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '1154-revision-v1', '', '', '2014-09-23 16:28:07', '2014-09-23 16:28:07', '', 1154, 'http://transitioning.olemiss.edu/1154-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
