(1554, 3, '2015-09-03 14:24:22', '2015-09-03 14:24:22', 'Welcome to the Transitioning to College Writing Symposium website, hosted by the Department of Writing and Rhetoric at the University of Mississippi. We hope you will join us for the fifth anniversary of our TCW Symposium!\n\n<strong>The <a href=\"http://transitioning.olemiss.edu/archive/symposium2014/program/\">program schedule</a> for this year\'s symposium is now available! We encourage you to register soon! Online registration ends September 23, 2015. After that, you may register at the door.\n</strong>\n\nTransitioning to College Writing is an annual symposium for writing teachers from college and high school settings in Mississippi and the Memphis areas. Attendees will gather on the University of Mississippi\'s Oxford, MS campus, and this year, we are looking forward to welcoming our visiting scholars: <a href=\"http://transitioning.olemiss.edu/staff-members/clint-gardner/\">Clint Gardner</a> (Salt Lake CC), <a href=\"http://transitioning.olemiss.edu/contributors/speakers/\">Cynthia A. Selfe</a> (The Ohio State U), and <a href=\"http://transitioning.olemiss.edu/contributors/speakers/\">Richard \"Dickie\" Selfe</a>, also of OSU.\n<h3>Welcome and Preview of the 2015 Transitioning to College Writing Symposium</h3>\n[responsive_vid]', 'Welcome!', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1103-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-09-03 14:24:22', '2015-09-03 14:24:22', '', 1103, 'http://transitioning.olemiss.edu/1103-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
